296
00:18:05,920 --> 00:18:06,920
No house buying, no loans.

297
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,119
No travel, no retirement plans.

298
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:09,119
Is this Wen Yitong?

299
00:18:10,079 --> 00:18:11,200
Is Fan Meijuan your mother?

300
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:11,880
