305
00:18:16,359 --> 00:18:17,720
She is in so much pain
that she can't move.

306
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:18,799
I called an ambulance for her.

307
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:20,640
We're heading to the People's Hospital.

308
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:22,039
The People's Hospital.

309
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,519
Hurry up.

310
00:18:34,359 --> 00:18:35,079
Mom!

311
00:18:35,079 --> 00:18:36,119
Hurry up!

312
00:18:38,519 --> 00:18:39,200
Are you a relative?

313
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,039
No.

314
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:41,440
No.

315
00:18:42,039 --> 00:18:43,200
Not this one.

316
00:18:46,599 --> 00:18:47,119
This one.

317
00:18:51,599 --> 00:18:52,599
We're here, Madam.

318
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:53,440
We're here.

319
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:55,640
Is this Fan Meijuan?

320
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:56,680
Mom.

321
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:57,640
Yitong.

322
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:58,279
Mom.

323
00:18:58,279 --> 00:18:59,000
Be careful.

324
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:00,680
Mom,

325
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:01,400
