326
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,519
- I fell.
- You're her family?

327
00:19:02,519 --> 00:19:03,160
I know.

328
00:19:03,279 --> 00:19:04,079
That's her bag.

329
00:19:04,079 --> 00:19:04,680
It's fine.

330
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:06,960
Be careful.

331
00:19:07,079 --> 00:19:08,200
Go check in and pay first.

332
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,920
I fell myself.

333
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,160
I fell myself.

334
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:14,000
I didn't call ambulance immediately

335
00:19:14,359 --> 00:19:15,039
because I was afraid

336
00:19:15,039 --> 00:19:16,160
someone would

337
00:19:16,839 --> 00:19:17,519
accuse me

338
00:19:17,519 --> 00:19:19,160
