339
00:19:19,640 --> 00:19:20,519
Please don't blame me.

340
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:22,759
To be honest,

341
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:26,039
I need to raise my daughter.

342
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:27,480
