353
00:19:56,279 --> 00:19:57,200
Sorry to take up your time.

354
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:58,440
I'll transfer you 5,000 yuan.

355
00:19:58,599 --> 00:19:59,960
I didn't help her for the money.

356
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:03,960
Old people shouldn't fall.

357
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,680
A hit to the head and they're gone.

358
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:09,400
I'll transfer you 10,000.

359
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:10,279
