360
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:11,599
I told you

361
00:20:11,599 --> 00:20:13,119
I didn't help her for the money.

362
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:16,559
I helped

363
00:20:16,559 --> 00:20:17,680
