366
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:26,359
She fell into the bathtub.

367
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:33,160
Thank you.

368
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,759
We're from the same hometown.

369
00:20:38,279 --> 00:20:39,480
