395
00:21:42,359 --> 00:21:43,680
Then I found it no longer a good deal.

396
00:21:43,839 --> 00:21:44,720
So I shut it down

397
00:21:44,799 --> 00:21:45,599
and went back to work.

398
00:21:45,799 --> 00:21:47,039
Either way, it's still making a living.

399
00:21:47,079 --> 00:21:47,759
Yeah.

400
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:49,839
You're here.

401
00:21:50,119 --> 00:21:50,559
Ms. Jiang

402
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:52,599
You're already eating?

403
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:53,880
I've eaten.

404
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:55,799
I don't know who made it for me,

405
00:21:55,799 --> 00:21:57,119
but it's really good.

406
00:21:57,559 --> 00:21:58,359
No chili, right?

407
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,079
No.

408
00:21:59,319 --> 00:22:00,200
I used to be a caregiver.

409
00:22:00,319 --> 00:22:01,240
I know what can be eaten

410
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:02,079
and what not.

411
00:22:02,279 --> 00:22:03,359
Jiang

412
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,359
