416
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:10,920
The hem was torn.

417
00:22:10,920 --> 00:22:11,559
I mended it.

418
00:22:11,799 --> 00:22:13,079
You're so good at this.

419
00:22:13,079 --> 00:22:14,400
I can't even tell where it was torn.

420
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:15,599
It looks brand new.

421
00:22:15,880 --> 00:22:17,440
And you even washed it.

422
00:22:17,559 --> 00:22:18,400
I bought two meals.

423
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:19,480
Have you eaten? Join me.

424
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,279
I already ate.

425
00:22:20,279 --> 00:22:20,920
One for each of us.

426
00:22:20,920 --> 00:22:21,400
I've eaten.

427
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:22,519
Time for your medicine.

428
00:22:22,519 --> 00:22:23,400
Eat with us first.

429
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:24,440
Apply this

430
00:22:24,759 --> 00:22:26,200
