431
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:27,519
Since she was wearing a dress,

432
00:22:27,880 --> 00:22:29,400
here and here are both swollen.

433
00:22:29,759 --> 00:22:30,920
She is shy,
so you apply it for her.

434
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,279
I'll clear the table.

435
00:22:32,279 --> 00:22:32,960
Okay.

436
00:22:33,759 --> 00:22:34,400
Done eating?

437
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:35,119
Done.

438
00:22:35,119 --> 00:22:35,960
I'll take these then.

439
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:36,880
Thank you.

440
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:38,799
You're welcome.

441
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:45,359
What's up?

442
00:22:45,599 --> 00:22:47,240
She is diligent,

443
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:48,920
and she cooks well.

444
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:50,640
Quick and good at cooking.

445
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:52,400
Got it.

446
00:22:53,920 --> 00:22:54,880
It's done, mom.

447
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:57,160
The doctor said it was not serious.

448
00:22:57,440 --> 00:22:58,640
We can go home after observation.

449
00:22:58,640 --> 00:22:59,799
Okay.

450
00:22:59,799 --> 00:23:00,400
That's good.

451
00:23:02,079 --> 00:23:02,680
Jiang,

452
00:23:03,519 --> 00:23:04,680
