453
00:23:04,799 --> 00:23:06,279
She said you were nice and diligent

454
00:23:06,279 --> 00:23:07,039
and you cooked well.

455
00:23:07,519 --> 00:23:08,079
Look.

456
00:23:08,200 --> 00:23:10,039
If you're free in the days to come,

457
00:23:10,039 --> 00:23:10,720
could you

458
00:23:10,720 --> 00:23:12,160
