459
00:23:12,279 --> 00:23:13,359
Recently, we've

460
00:23:13,359 --> 00:23:13,920
been very busy.

461
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:14,839
We're a bit tied up.

462
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:15,920
It would be great if you could come.

463
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:17,480
I am actually not very busy.

464
00:23:17,480 --> 00:23:18,640
But I won't be at home...

465
00:23:18,839 --> 00:23:19,480
Please, just come.

466
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:20,240
If you're free,

467
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:21,119
you can just come.

468
00:23:21,279 --> 00:23:22,119
Just say yes.

469
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:23,079
Excuse me.

470
00:23:23,580 --> 00:23:24,160
(Zhan)

471
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:25,359
I'll take a call.

472
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:42,240
Yu Ming.

473
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:45,720
You like her?

474
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:47,400
No.

475
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:49,279
