476
00:23:49,319 --> 00:23:49,920
Is it okay, Mom?

477
00:23:50,559 --> 00:23:50,960
Alright.

478
00:23:52,039 --> 00:23:52,720
Done eating?

479
00:23:55,079 --> 00:23:55,640
Don't move.

480
00:23:56,039 --> 00:23:56,559
Let him do it.

481
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:57,400
I'll do it.

482
00:24:01,079 --> 00:24:01,519
You

483
00:24:02,559 --> 00:24:04,160
and Shiqi...

484
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:06,680
I'm just staying here for a few days.

485
00:24:06,799 --> 00:24:07,920
I'll move out once I find a place.

486
00:24:08,920 --> 00:24:09,640
No worries.

487
00:24:10,079 --> 00:24:11,759
Stay as long as you want.

488
00:24:11,839 --> 00:24:13,160
Shiqi likes having people around.

489
00:24:13,319 --> 00:24:13,839
The liveliness.

490
00:24:14,319 --> 00:24:14,759
Right?

491
00:24:17,079 --> 00:24:17,720
Is it usually

492
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:19,440
