493
00:24:19,480 --> 00:24:19,960
No.

494
00:24:20,119 --> 00:24:21,000
Not lively.

495
00:24:21,759 --> 00:24:22,160
Yeah.

496
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:23,839
It's really quiet.

497
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:24,799
You only miss

498
00:24:24,799 --> 00:24:25,960
what you don't have.

499
00:24:27,839 --> 00:24:28,960
Shiqi

500
00:24:29,319 --> 00:24:30,640
seems to be outgoing.

501
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,960
In fact, he is an introvert.

502
00:24:32,279 --> 00:24:33,359
And he is very reserved.

503
00:24:33,799 --> 00:24:34,839
When I was in high school,

504
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:36,119
a lot of guys chased me.

505
00:24:36,559 --> 00:24:37,559
So he went to my school

506
00:24:37,559 --> 00:24:38,920
and beat them all up.

507
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,519
He even returned all the gifts

508
00:24:40,519 --> 00:24:41,440
they'd given me.

509
00:24:41,759 --> 00:24:42,440
Seriously.

510
00:24:42,519 --> 00:24:43,480
He really cares about you.

511
00:24:43,559 --> 00:24:44,920
He cares about you even more.

512
00:24:45,079 --> 00:24:46,599
When I come alone,

513
00:24:47,039 --> 00:24:48,079
