514
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:49,759
What do you want to drink?

515
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:50,440
I'll get it.

516
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:51,079
Anything is fine.

517
00:24:59,880 --> 00:25:00,680
This girl is not bad.

518
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:01,519
Lock it down.

519
00:25:03,759 --> 00:25:05,079
Don't talk nonsense.

520
00:25:05,519 --> 00:25:06,559
She was driven out by her landlord.

521
00:25:06,559 --> 00:25:07,519
I wanted to help her.

522
00:25:07,559 --> 00:25:08,880
She is just sharing the place.

523
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:10,200
