526
00:25:15,200 --> 00:25:15,640
Keep lying.

527
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:16,519
Go ahead.

528
00:25:17,119 --> 00:25:18,279
Don't say I didn't warn you.

529
00:25:18,759 --> 00:25:19,559
Don't miss out.

530
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,759
The way her hair is done,

531
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:33,119
that curvy style.

532
00:25:33,480 --> 00:25:35,880
It's a 100% match.

533
00:25:36,079 --> 00:25:36,599
No.

534
00:25:36,599 --> 00:25:37,559
There are just a few

535
00:25:37,559 --> 00:25:38,680
