536
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:40,160
There are 700 million women in China.

537
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:41,279
200 million wear it like that.

538
00:25:41,319 --> 00:25:42,599
That's way too broad.

539
00:25:42,759 --> 00:25:44,200
I thought about that too.

540
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:46,279
But her body type matches too.

541
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:48,839
Anyway, I just felt she was so familiar
when I saw her.

542
00:25:48,839 --> 00:25:49,960
I felt like

543
00:25:50,079 --> 00:25:51,480
I was returning to that night.

544
00:25:51,599 --> 00:25:51,880
Fine.

545
00:25:52,119 --> 00:25:53,319
Let me change the perspective.

546
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:55,119
She came from nowhere

547
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:56,960
and saved your mom.

548
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:58,440
Even if it was coincidental,

549
00:25:58,440 --> 00:25:59,839
fine. She helped, end of story.

550
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:01,599
But then she stuck around
for follow-up care.

551
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:02,519
That feel calculated.

552
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:03,839
Is there a possibility

553
00:26:03,839 --> 00:26:04,359
that she's just

554
00:26:04,359 --> 00:26:05,960
warm-hearted,

555
00:26:06,119 --> 00:26:06,519
like you?

556
00:26:06,519 --> 00:26:07,640
I'll come later.

557
00:26:09,759 --> 00:26:11,359
I found someone called Jiang Juan.

558
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:13,400
Take a look and see if it's her.

559
00:26:14,039 --> 00:26:14,680
That's her.

560
00:26:14,680 --> 00:26:15,680
Yes, it's her.

561
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:16,880
She has worked here

562
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:17,920
for seven or eight years.

563
00:26:18,119 --> 00:26:19,200
She's our top caregiver.

564
00:26:19,440 --> 00:26:21,119
You need an appointment.
Everyone wants her.

565
00:26:21,759 --> 00:26:22,400
Let me tell you,

566
00:26:22,559 --> 00:26:24,400
not only does she
cook amazing Sichuan food,

567
00:26:24,519 --> 00:26:25,319
but she's also

568
00:26:25,319 --> 00:26:26,359
very creative.

569
00:26:26,559 --> 00:26:27,400
She came up with

570
00:26:27,519 --> 00:26:28,720
games for the elderly

571
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:29,880
to help prevent dementia.

572
00:26:30,359 --> 00:26:31,640
You're really lucky

573
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:32,920
to have her.

574
00:26:37,799 --> 00:26:40,720
My mother-in-law has a sharp eye.

575
00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:43,119
Looks like I really misjudged her.

576
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:38,799
Look at Ouyang.

577
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:39,799
Isn't this the first time?

578
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:41,480
In the past, whenever
you were in trouble,

579
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:42,720
he'd lend his help.

580
00:27:42,799 --> 00:27:43,279
Why is he

581
00:27:43,279 --> 00:27:44,160
ignoring you this time?

582
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:45,440
You were exhausting yourself,

583
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:46,559
yet he just stood by and watched.

584
00:27:46,559 --> 00:27:47,200
What's this called?

585
00:27:47,240 --> 00:27:49,160
That's "hope your buddy does well,

586
00:27:49,279 --> 00:27:50,480
but not better than you."

587
00:27:50,559 --> 00:27:51,640
Isn't Jiajia

588
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:52,640
jealous of you?

589
00:27:52,799 --> 00:27:53,799
Jiajia isn't.

590
00:27:53,799 --> 00:27:54,720
You know our relationship.

591
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:55,799
We've been through thick and thin

592
00:27:55,799 --> 00:27:56,559
for over a decade.

593
00:27:56,599 --> 00:27:58,119
Ouyang and I have saved
each other's lives.

594
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:01,279
♪Work hard and make money♪

595
00:28:01,400 --> 00:28:02,400
(Qian Weijie)

596
00:28:02,400 --> 00:28:02,920
Who is it?

597
00:28:04,079 --> 00:28:04,559
It's him.

598
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:06,240
This guy gets jealous.

599
00:28:06,359 --> 00:28:07,359
It's Qian Weijie?

600
00:28:08,119 --> 00:28:08,640
Reject it.

601
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:09,960
Okay, reject it.

602
00:28:10,039 --> 00:28:10,720
I'm getting one too.

603
00:28:10,839 --> 00:28:11,559
Who is this?

604
00:28:12,039 --> 00:28:13,200
Ouyang is a good guy.

605
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:14,519
He is very kind.

606
00:28:14,559 --> 00:28:16,240
He just doesn't know
how to express himself.

607
00:28:16,359 --> 00:28:17,079
He doesn't want us

608
00:28:17,079 --> 00:28:18,160
to touch this money.

609
00:28:19,519 --> 00:28:20,359
Here you go again.

610
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:21,720
Aren't they tired?

611
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:23,160
Turn off the phone.

612
00:28:23,359 --> 00:28:24,240
Here it comes again.

613
00:28:25,079 --> 00:28:25,680
I'll turn it off.

614
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,279
Turn it off.

615
00:28:35,359 --> 00:28:35,960
Hello.

616
00:28:36,319 --> 00:28:37,359
The number you dialed

617
00:28:37,359 --> 00:28:38,839
cannot be reached now.

618
00:28:52,799 --> 00:28:53,559
Don't waste food.

619
00:28:55,559 --> 00:28:56,839
Look how stingy you are.

620
00:28:57,559 --> 00:28:59,119
Like it's costing you a fortune.

621
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:00,519
In this lifetime,

622
00:29:00,519 --> 00:29:01,400
you'll never amount to much.

623
00:29:20,960 --> 00:29:21,519
Hello.

624
00:29:21,839 --> 00:29:23,000
The number you dialed

625
00:29:23,119 --> 00:29:24,359
cannot be reached now.

626
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:25,480
Look how pathetic you are.

627
00:29:25,559 --> 00:29:26,400
You heartless,

628
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,720
ungrateful wretch!

629
00:29:29,440 --> 00:29:30,599
Now that you have money,

630
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:31,559
you're a ruthless fat cat.

631
00:29:31,599 --> 00:29:32,440
Sooner or later,

632
00:29:32,440 --> 00:29:33,079
a big truck

633
00:29:33,079 --> 00:29:34,240
will run over your head.

634
00:29:34,279 --> 00:29:35,039
Crush you to death!

635
00:29:36,519 --> 00:29:37,200
Mr. Yu,

636
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:38,200
you must be busy.

637
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,680
You didn't answer my calls.

638
00:29:39,680 --> 00:29:40,799
Here's the thing.

639
00:29:40,839 --> 00:29:42,039
About what I told you before,

640
00:29:42,079 --> 00:29:43,200
now everything is in place.

641
00:29:43,319 --> 00:29:44,119
Just waiting on you.

642
00:29:44,119 --> 00:29:44,880
When

643
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:45,839
you have time,

644
00:29:45,839 --> 00:29:47,039
just come through for us.

645
00:29:47,359 --> 00:29:48,039
Hit me back

646
00:29:48,079 --> 00:29:48,960
when you're free.

647
00:29:55,119 --> 00:29:55,599
Boss,

648
00:29:55,960 --> 00:29:57,559
have they moved the money
to somewhere else?

649
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:25,960
Yu Ming.

650
00:30:29,079 --> 00:30:30,640
Our noodle shop was doing fine.

651
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:31,400
It was making money.

652
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:32,440
Why sell it?

653
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:34,759
The noodle shop, or 30 million.

654
00:30:34,799 --> 00:30:35,519
Which one do you pick?

655
00:30:35,559 --> 00:30:36,400
I want 30 million.

656
00:30:36,559 --> 00:30:38,039
See? You want the money too.

657
00:30:38,119 --> 00:30:39,119
Now I'm watching them

658
00:30:39,279 --> 00:30:40,039
and running the shop.

659
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:41,079
I'm too swamped now.

660
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:43,079
Are you out of your mind?

661
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:44,319
What if we can't find the money?

662
00:30:45,759 --> 00:30:46,440
We'll cross

663
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:47,279
that bridge later.

664
00:30:47,599 --> 00:30:49,000
We took such a huge risk

665
00:30:49,039 --> 00:30:49,880
to come to Luzhou

666
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:51,160
just to open a restaurant?

667
00:30:51,240 --> 00:30:52,119
Of course not.

668
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,839
You keep your eyes on Unit 505.

669
00:30:55,039 --> 00:30:56,440
I'll keep an eye on their place.

670
00:30:57,519 --> 00:30:58,200
We will definitely

671
00:30:58,200 --> 00:30:59,000
get the money.

672
00:30:59,359 --> 00:30:59,720
Yes.

673
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:01,480
Definitely.

674
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:14,720
This one and the noodles I cook,

675
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:15,839
which one's better?

676
00:31:16,960 --> 00:31:18,240
Of course yours is better.

677
00:31:18,839 --> 00:31:20,480
There's no comparison.

678
00:31:21,079 --> 00:31:21,960
I don't eat it.

679
00:31:27,079 --> 00:31:28,359
After the restaurant is closed,

680
00:31:29,359 --> 00:31:31,079
it won't be so easy to eat my noodles.

681
00:31:31,240 --> 00:31:31,559
Then

682
00:31:31,559 --> 00:31:32,839
I'll have some more these days.

683
00:31:33,359 --> 00:31:34,119
Make more for me.

684
00:31:34,759 --> 00:31:35,920
I'll only eat noodles these days.

685
00:31:36,119 --> 00:31:36,799
Just go for it.

686
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:39,720
You fool.

687
00:32:09,440 --> 00:32:09,960
Zhu,

688
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:11,880
come and look.

689
00:32:13,880 --> 00:32:14,400
What's up?

690
00:32:14,680 --> 00:32:15,119
Let me look.

691
00:32:16,880 --> 00:32:17,680
Did we dig through?

692
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:22,440
We did.

693
00:32:28,680 --> 00:32:29,519
Step back.

694
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:30,400
Step back.

695
00:32:45,680 --> 00:32:46,079
Zhu,

696
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:47,960
did we dig into someone's grave?

697
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:49,960
This doesn't look like a basement.

698
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:56,039
If you want to hide

699
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:57,640
that much money,

700
00:32:58,440 --> 00:32:59,200
you have to dig

701
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:00,319
really deep.

702
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:01,559
Why don't we just

703
00:33:01,559 --> 00:33:02,599
hire a professional team

704
00:33:02,599 --> 00:33:03,680
to do the digging?

705
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:04,480
When it's almost done,

706
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:05,319
we take over.

707
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:05,880
No way.

708
00:33:06,720 --> 00:33:08,119
We can't let that many people know.

709
00:33:08,599 --> 00:33:09,839
Who would dig

710
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:11,839
a big hole in their basement?

711
00:33:12,359 --> 00:33:13,799
We can't leave any trace.

712
00:33:14,720 --> 00:33:15,359
If it takes a week,

713
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,160
I'll dig it myself.

714
00:33:18,240 --> 00:33:18,759
A month,

715
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:20,519
I'll still dig it myself.

716
00:33:21,519 --> 00:33:22,119
A year,

717
00:33:22,559 --> 00:33:24,039
I'm digging it myself!

718
00:33:33,599 --> 00:33:34,000
Zhu.

719
00:33:34,519 --> 00:33:35,039
That's money!

720
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:43,519
The money is not up there.

721
00:33:44,519 --> 00:33:45,319
It's here.

722
00:33:58,119 --> 00:33:58,519
Zhu,

723
00:33:58,640 --> 00:33:59,079
be careful!

724
00:34:03,079 --> 00:34:03,640
Are you okay?

725
00:34:03,920 --> 00:34:04,480
I'm fine.

726
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:05,440
I'm fine.

727
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:49,679
Go!

728
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:50,880
Quick, go!

729
00:35:19,239 --> 00:35:19,599
Zhu!

730
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:20,960
Hurry!

731
00:35:32,239 --> 00:35:33,199
Go!

732
00:35:39,519 --> 00:35:40,239
Turn off the lights.

733
00:35:40,719 --> 00:35:41,320
Turn off!

734
00:35:50,719 --> 00:35:51,280
No one.

735
00:35:51,719 --> 00:35:52,360
No one's coming.

736
00:36:04,400 --> 00:36:05,519
So much money.

737
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:08,159
The money covered two whole walls.

738
00:36:09,199 --> 00:36:10,280
If someone gave me that,

739
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,639
I'd call them daddy on the spot.

740
00:36:12,239 --> 00:36:12,679
Wait.

741
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:14,719
Something's wrong.

742
00:36:16,039 --> 00:36:16,880
The money wasn't

743
00:36:17,719 --> 00:36:18,880
supposed to be in the wall?

744
00:36:19,199 --> 00:36:19,719
Yeah.

745
00:36:21,079 --> 00:36:22,360
We built those walls.

746
00:36:25,960 --> 00:36:26,639
So how is there

747
00:36:26,639 --> 00:36:27,559
so much money underground?

748
00:36:27,679 --> 00:36:28,480
Hu Deshuai

749
00:36:29,039 --> 00:36:30,000
has hidden so much money,

750
00:36:30,920 --> 00:36:32,599
but won't pay us back what he owes.

751
00:36:32,599 --> 00:36:33,320
I told you,

752
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,280
Hu Deshuai is no good.

753
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:35,719
I said don't work for him,

754
00:36:35,719 --> 00:36:37,119
but you just wouldn't listen.

755
00:36:37,239 --> 00:36:37,599
See?

756
00:36:37,599 --> 00:36:38,119
Well,

757
00:36:38,119 --> 00:36:39,559
when did you ever say that?

758
00:36:39,559 --> 00:36:40,239
Just at that time,

759
00:36:40,239 --> 00:36:41,800
when we were...

760
00:36:42,159 --> 00:36:42,920
Stop nagging.

761
00:36:43,199 --> 00:36:43,719
Keep it down.

762
00:36:44,639 --> 00:36:45,480
He already saw us.

763
00:36:45,519 --> 00:36:46,079
What do we do?

764
00:36:46,199 --> 00:36:46,840
I don't know.

765
00:36:47,239 --> 00:36:48,039
What's that attitude?

766
00:36:55,719 --> 00:36:56,519
How about we go home?

767
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:57,760
We leave tonight.

768
00:36:58,039 --> 00:36:58,679
Go home?

769
00:36:59,079 --> 00:36:59,880
We won't take the money?

770
00:37:00,079 --> 00:37:01,000
You still want the money?

771
00:37:01,199 --> 00:37:02,199
Worry about your life first.

772
00:37:02,199 --> 00:37:03,719
Keep your voice down.

773
00:37:04,039 --> 00:37:05,320
What if they call the cops?

774
00:37:05,559 --> 00:37:06,760
The tunnel entrance is right there.

775
00:37:06,960 --> 00:37:07,800
They'll find us for sure.

776
00:37:09,400 --> 00:37:10,480
I'm calling the shots today.

777
00:37:11,039 --> 00:37:12,119
San and I will pack up.

778
00:37:12,199 --> 00:37:12,960
You go buy the tickets.

779
00:37:13,480 --> 00:37:14,119
San, let's go.

780
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:18,559
Go, San.

781
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:23,360
How can you sleep at a time like this?

782
00:37:23,639 --> 00:37:24,599
You've got some nerve.

783
00:37:25,639 --> 00:37:26,079
San!

784
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:28,159
San!

785
00:37:29,760 --> 00:37:30,119
San!

786
00:37:30,599 --> 00:37:31,000
Zhu.

787
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:32,400
What's wrong with San?

788
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:34,800
San!

789
00:37:36,079 --> 00:37:36,519
San!

790
00:37:38,159 --> 00:37:38,639
San!

791
00:37:45,920 --> 00:37:46,960
100, take it away.

792
00:37:54,180 --> 00:37:54,900
(500,000)

793
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:21,280
30 million here, and 30 million there.

794
00:38:22,039 --> 00:38:22,440
Well,

795
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,440
Lamp's Aladdin?

796
00:38:24,440 --> 00:38:25,039
Well, I...

797
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:26,039
Aladdin's Lamp.

798
00:38:26,239 --> 00:38:27,719
About those three who dug the tunnel,

799
00:38:28,039 --> 00:38:29,559
think hard. Remember

800
00:38:29,639 --> 00:38:30,840
the two who broke in the other day?

801
00:38:31,079 --> 00:38:32,280
Are any of these three those two?

802
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:33,800
I don't think so.

803
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:35,639
Look now.

804
00:38:35,639 --> 00:38:36,840
The one on motorcycle chasing us,

805
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:38,000
the ones who climbed the wall,

806
00:38:38,119 --> 00:38:38,960
the ones digging tunnels.

807
00:38:39,119 --> 00:38:40,760
All came for this money.

808
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:42,119
Look how dangerous we are now.

809
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:42,920
What do we do?

810
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:44,000
Who knows if there's more

811
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:44,639
coming?

812
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:46,480
We have to figure out the situation.

813
00:38:46,599 --> 00:38:48,360
What's really going on here?

814
00:38:48,559 --> 00:38:49,960
Does Chen Zinuo know this 30 million?

815
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:50,880
I mean this 30 million.

816
00:38:51,119 --> 00:38:52,360
I don't know.

817
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:53,880
It's hard to say.

818
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:55,760
Maybe there wasn't enough room upstairs,

819
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:57,000
so they put more underneath.

820
00:38:57,159 --> 00:38:58,400
Or like what my mom said,

821
00:38:59,000 --> 00:38:59,599
you can't

822
00:38:59,719 --> 00:39:00,960
put all the eggs in the same basket.

823
00:39:01,199 --> 00:39:02,400
My heart's racing right now.

824
00:39:03,239 --> 00:39:05,000
We really have to figure out

825
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:06,440
whether there is more money or not.

826
00:39:06,519 --> 00:39:07,639
What if more turns up?

827
00:39:07,639 --> 00:39:08,840
We can't handle all this now.

828
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:10,519
This is just too much.

829
00:39:14,760 --> 00:39:15,639
It's already 4:30 a.m.

830
00:39:15,719 --> 00:39:17,440
I'm going home to check on my mom.

831
00:39:17,599 --> 00:39:18,960
She just got out of the hospital.

832
00:39:19,119 --> 00:39:19,639
I'll come too.

833
00:39:19,639 --> 00:39:20,239
No, you stay.

834
00:39:20,239 --> 00:39:20,960
There's so much money here.

835
00:39:20,960 --> 00:39:22,039
Someone has to watch it.

836
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:23,159
You're not going anywhere.

837
00:39:23,159 --> 00:39:23,920
Watch this place.

838
00:39:27,519 --> 00:39:28,840
Pull up

839
00:39:28,840 --> 00:39:29,599
that old case

840
00:39:29,599 --> 00:39:30,239
about the homeowner

841
00:39:30,480 --> 00:39:31,360
and go through it.

842
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:32,760
Maybe you can find something.

843
00:39:37,679 --> 00:39:38,400
Don't go.

844
00:39:48,039 --> 00:39:48,519
Yu Ming,

845
00:39:48,679 --> 00:39:50,159
you're just a big scammer.

846
00:39:50,400 --> 00:39:51,159
An ungrateful wretch.

847
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:53,280
If I fed a stray dog,

848
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:54,519
at least it would be grateful.

849
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:56,039
I was so fool

850
00:39:56,039 --> 00:39:56,960
to pay your debts.

851
00:39:56,960 --> 00:39:57,800
Just begging to be used.

852
00:39:58,239 --> 00:39:59,320
Pathetic, that's what I am.

853
00:39:59,599 --> 00:40:00,039
Just you wait!

854
00:40:03,599 --> 00:40:04,960
Don't rush me!

855
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:16,920
Yu Ming!

856
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:19,000
Yu Ming!

857
00:40:20,159 --> 00:40:21,559
Yu Ming, I know you're home.

858
00:40:21,559 --> 00:40:22,599
Come on, open the door.

859
00:40:22,599 --> 00:40:23,400
I won't beat you.

860
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:23,880
Yu Ming,

861
00:40:24,079 --> 00:40:25,159
about investing in those coins,

862
00:40:25,159 --> 00:40:26,519
you said you'd invest three days ago,

863
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:27,679
then two days ago,

864
00:40:27,679 --> 00:40:28,880
then yesterday.

865
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:30,079
Where's the money?

866
00:40:30,159 --> 00:40:31,239
Come out. Let's sort this out.

867
00:40:31,239 --> 00:40:31,639
Okay?

868
00:40:31,719 --> 00:40:32,920
I sold my kidney

869
00:40:32,920 --> 00:40:33,480
to pay

870
00:40:33,480 --> 00:40:34,679
that loan shark off for you.

871
00:40:34,719 --> 00:40:35,440
The last 20,000 yuan?

872
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:36,360
I borrowed it for you.

873
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:37,320
Whether you like it or not,

874
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:38,599
you owe me money now.

875
00:40:38,599 --> 00:40:39,800
I'm your creditor, your know.

876
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:40,519
Yu Ming,

877
00:40:40,960 --> 00:40:41,679
no matter what,

878
00:40:41,679 --> 00:40:42,599
we're partners.

879
00:40:42,599 --> 00:40:43,280
Do you understand?

880
00:40:43,559 --> 00:40:44,559
You're putting

881
00:40:44,559 --> 00:40:45,159
in the money.

882
00:40:45,159 --> 00:40:45,719
You hear me?

883
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:46,400
Yu Ming,

884
00:40:46,719 --> 00:40:47,440
I can see you.

885
00:40:47,519 --> 00:40:48,360
Open the door quickly!

886
00:40:48,920 --> 00:40:49,400
Yu Ming!

887
00:40:50,199 --> 00:40:50,800
Yu Ming!

888
