899
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,559
Bro!

900
00:41:19,719 --> 00:41:20,679
Wait a moment, let me think.

901
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:21,199
Let me think.

902
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:23,199
